 These sufficient conditions are satisfied by some physical\nfields, which are presented as examples.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Oct 2001 19:54:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Oct 2001 20:01:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 25 Feb 2002 13:09:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
